title: mushroom stroganoff

needs:
 - 300g mixed mushroom, chopped
 - 1 onion, finely chopped
 - 3 tbsp sour cream
 - 150ml stock
 - 1 tbsp Worcestershire sauce
 - 1 tbsp paprika
 - 2 garlic cloves, crushed
 - small bunch parsley, roughly chopped

steps:
 - fry the onion.
 - add the paprika and garlic.
 - add the mushrooms.
 - add the stock and Worcestershire sauce.
 - bring to boil and bubble for 5 minutes.
 - stir in the sour cream and parsley.

notes:
 - https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/mushroom-stroganoff
